- [ ] Minimum 8px spacing between adjacent targets
- [ ] No accidental taps on wrong element
- [ ] Works with accessibility settings enabled","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-29T22:28:41.444129486-05:00","updated_at":"2025-12-30T02:19:54.437518903-05:00","closed_at":"2025-12-30T02:19:54.437518903-05:00","close_reason":"Touch target audit complete: Fixed TOC items to 44px min-height, Tabs component to 44px, close buttons from 32px to 44px (size-11), and button sm/icon-sm variants from 32px to 40px. Added touch-manipulation CSS to interactive elements. Build and all 641 tests pass.","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"brenner_bot-ef3","depends_on_id":"brenner_bot-qka","type":"blocks","created_at":"2025-12-29T22:29:18.174254479-05:00","created_by":"daemon","metadata":"{}"}]}
